456f3806caadf99f61660ca5be6ba728","tid":1099254,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab3b46ef751c7ae9caa7051665b5b6e126b2d569","tid":1099254,"uid":41923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"90幾萬的話算好多下<br />\n6x伙連幾個地鋪<br />\n我估每戶夾唔超過十萬<br />\n<br />\n你計過數覺得個價錢啱位置啱的話都唔算太大問題 <br />\n當然有得揀的話就揀伙數較多既單支"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"數學家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:40:22.000Z","msg":"我講緊大維修每戶夾唔超過十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩數學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"識人做ngo 幫法團同政府申請支助做大維修。聽過有單支大維修每戶30萬（已經減左政府支助再除）<br />\n<br />\n買單支唔係問題，但要樓換樓...你加下可能比到十萬8萬，但個大維修可能係十年後。到時你又比唔比到先，到時唔只十萬8 萬...<br />\n另一樣野係電梯e 尾野，一但收例，到時又洗一不大。<br />\n<br />\n同埋戶戶比到十萬8萬 就好lo, 有幾戶 老人家比唔到，又要loop 好耐，又small claim 又傾......又拖一年半年<br />\n<br />\n再做過報價又每人夾多一萬幾千......"},{"pid":"18a45877d7bf95246ea4af9a14e06e66a3c794c4","tid":1099254,"uid":41923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f