價+硬食貴管理費買新樓同半新樓<br />\n<br />\n換樓點會換唔到 講到無人買咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人買就代表有人賣 何來換唔到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你搵市區單支既成交價去睇 睇下個呎價走勢同屋苑比較個升幅 <br />\n你2015年求買一間深水埗單支 今日都可以高至少40%賣走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話單支維修費貴<br />\n但新樓管理費一樣好貴<br />\n300-400呎新樓可能已經要$1500-$2000<br />\n一年就兩萬幾<br />\n你今日比得起兩萬幾<br />\n他日呢？十年廿年後變成五六萬一年呢？你仲比唔比得起？"},{"pid":"530df476223ba9c198090af32487191a165684f3","tid":1099254,"uid":89642,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18a45877d7bf95246ea4af9a14e06e66a3c794c4","tid":1099254,"uid":41923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fb11d0df7bd328aae5cabe0c08b0e25e6797995","tid":1099254,"uid":89642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ba095bf81b33e353265da033ccab90f44fcd0200","tid":1099254,"uid":41923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T13:40:22.000Z","msg":"我講緊大維修每戶夾唔超過十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩數學家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019